milestones.description: Peter Kirsten has broken the record for most sixes (7) in ODIs for SA, going past Jonty Rhodes's 6
Peter Kirsten and Cullinan's 85-run partnership is SA's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 79 between Peter Kirsten and Richardson
This is the highest match aggregate (475) involving teams South Africa & New Zealand in ODIs
